               <note type="editions">Critical edition by ʿAbd al-ʿAzīz al-Manṣūb, based on mss. from the MIAS archive. Published by al-Qudus, Cairo, 2018. Critical edition, plus a translation into Urdu by the Ibn ʿArabī Foundation (Rawalpindi, Pakistan, 2008). Ed. Abrār Aḥmad Shāhī. Not an official critical edition, but the Arabic text produced by Gilis alongside his French translation Le Livre du Mîm, du Wâw et du Nūn (Paris, 2002) is taken from an excellent ms. – Shehit Ali 2813, written by Ayyūb b. Badr and read in front of IA. Another edition has been completed by Pablo Beneito but not yet published.</note>
